	<LongDescription>
Prevents cars from being spawned with trailers. This option must be enabled in the settings menu, and can be switched on/off at any time.

Additionally, there is a button to remove all existing trailers from the map.

Preventing vehicles from using trailers may impact gameplay because trailers increase the storage and passenger space for vehicles. This effect is unresearched.
